        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2 Verified-1\n\nWe cannot just ignore all of the test cases. They are there for a reason. We need to fix the embedded cassandra issue. ONAP requires a certain percentage of test cases and removing these will make us drop below the percentage. The issue with embedded cassandra has been documented here: https://github.com/jsevellec/cassandra-unit/pull/256\n\nwe just need to figure out how to incorporate the changes to embedded cassandra into our test code",
